        <h1>Parameter control: Setting up the function</h1>
        <p>To set critical parameter control modes:</p>
        <ol start="1" style="list-style: decimal;margin-top: 0cm;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p" value="1">
                <p><b style="font-weight: bold;">Set the list of critical parameters </b>(max 5000) to be monitored. Either single devices or device models can be selected.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="p" value="2">
                <p><b style="font-weight: bold;">Set notification modes</b>, indicating the control interval, addressees and whether notifications should be sent at the end of the control interval for each change (<i>single notification</i>) or if a single notification should be sent for all changes (<i>cumulative notification</i>). Select any PlantVisor PRO users who have parameter editing permission. Changes made by a PlantVisorPRO user with editing permissions do not generate notifications.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="p" value="3">
                <p><b style="font-weight: bold;">Enabling notifications</b>.</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <h2>Set the list of critical parameters</h2>
        <ol start="1" style="list-style: decimal;margin-top: 0cm;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p" value="1">
                <p>Open the <b>Parameters</b> page: </p>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <p class="Image">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/ControlloParametri_file/image030_600x288.jpg" style="border-style: none;border-style: none;width: 600;height: 288;" border="0" />
        </p>
        <ol start="2" style="margin-top: 0cm;list-style: decimal;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p-InlineNormal19" value="2">
                <p class="InlineNormal19">Select <b>Devices</b> to select parameters one device at a time. In the device list <b>[1]</b> double-click the selected device: all variables that can be monitored appear in the variable list <b>[2]</b>.</p>
            </li>
            <ul style="list-style: decimal;" type="1">
                <ol start="1" style="list-style: lower-roman;list-style-type: lower-roman;">
                    <li class="p-InlineNormal17" value="1">
                        <p class="InlineNormal17">Or select <b>Device models  </b>to select parameters for all devices of a certain type. All devices in the selected model appear in the device list <b>[1]</b> and all variables that can be monitored appear in the variable list <b>[2]</b>.</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </ul>
            <li class="p-InlineNormal19" value="3">
                <p class="InlineNormal19">Select one or more variables and click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/addsmall_on_black.png" style="width: 19px;height: 19px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="19" height="19" border="0" />: the variables are added to the list <b>[3]</b>. </p>
            </li>
            <li class="p" value="4">
                <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/save_button.png" style="width: 24px;height: 28px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="24" height="28" border="0" /><b>Save [4]</b> to save the list</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <table style="width: 100%;border-left-color: #000000;border-left-width: 1px;border-right-color: #000000;border-right-width: 1px;background-color: #c0c0c0;border-spacing: 0px;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#C0C0C0" width="100%">
            <col style="width: 6.855%;" />
            <col style="width: 93.145%;" />
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 6.855%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-width: 2px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" valign="middle" width="6.855%">
                    <p class="Note">
                        <img src="../Resources/Images/AAinfo.gif" style="border: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />
                    </p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 93.145%;padding-right: 1px;padding-left: 1px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 2px;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" width="93.145%">
                    <p class="Note" style="font-weight: normal;">To select adjacent variables, hold down the SHIFT key and select the first and last variables in the selection. </p>
                    <p class="Note" style="font-weight: normal;">To select several variables, hold down the CTRL key. To delete a variable, click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/removesmall_on_black.png" style="border: none;width: 19px;height: 19px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="19" height="19" border="0" /></p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <h2>Setting notification modes</h2>
        <ol start="1" style="list-style: decimal;margin-top: 0cm;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p" value="1">
                <p>Open the <b>Notification</b> page: </p>
            </li>
            <p class="Image">
                <img src="../Resources/Images/ControlloParametri_file/image036_EN_499x312.jpg" style="float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;width: 499;height: 312;" border="0" />
            </p>
        </ol>
        <ol start="2" style="list-style: decimal;margin-top: 0cm;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p-InlineNormal19" value="2">
                <p class="InlineNormal19">Select the appropriate interval</p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-InlineNormal19" value="3">
                <p class="InlineNormal19">Enter a name for device keyboards (default <b>DeviceKeyboard</b>)</p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-InlineNormal19" value="4">
                <p class="InlineNormal19">Specify the type of notification (one for each change or a cumulative one for all changes in the interval)</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <div style="padding: 5.0pt 0cm 5.0pt 0cm;background-color: #cccccc;border-top-color: #000000;border-top-style: solid;border-bottom-color: #000000;border-bottom-style: solid;border-top-width: 1pt;border-bottom-width: 1pt;width: 100%;float: none;">
            <p>
                <img src="../Resources/Images/AAinfo.gif" style="width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />&#160; Registrations always concern a single variable.</p>
        </div>
        <ol start="5" style="list-style: decimal;margin-top: 0cm;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p-InlineNormal19" value="5">
                <p class="InlineNormal19">Select one or more notification addressees and click <img src="../Resources/Images/dbllistbox/arrowdx_on.png" style="width: 54px;height: 19px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="54" height="19" border="0" /><b>[1]</b>: addressees are added to the list  <b>[2]</b></p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-InlineNormal19" value="6">
                <p class="InlineNormal19">Select one or more PlantVisor PRO user profiles to be authorized and click<img src="../Resources/Images/dbllistbox/arrowdx_on.png" style="width: 54px;height: 19px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="54" height="19" border="0" />: profiles are added to the list <b>[3]</b>. </p>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <div style="border-top: solid #000000 1.0pt;border-left: none;border-bottom: solid #000000 1.0pt;border-right: none;padding: 5.0pt 0cm 5.0pt 0cm;float: none;width: 100%;background-color: #cccccc;">
            <p>
                <img src="../Resources/Images/AAinfo.gif" style="width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />Changes made by these profile users do not generate any registration or notification.</p>
        </div>
        <ol start="1" style="list-style: decimal;margin-top: 0cm;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li value="1">&#160;</li>
        </ol>
        <ol start="7" style="list-style: decimal;margin-top: 0cm;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p" value="7">
                <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/save_button.png" style="width: 24px;height: 28px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="24" height="28" border="0" /><b>Save [4]</b> to save entered data.</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <h2>Enabling/disabling notifications</h2>
        <p>Notifications must be enabled. They may need to be temporarily disabled although still recorded in the log.</p>
        <ol start="7" style="list-style: decimal;margin-top: 0cm;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li value="7">&#160;</li>
        </ol>
        <ol start="1" style="list-style: decimal;margin-top: 0cm;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p" value="1">
                <p>Open the <b>Notification</b> page: </p>
            </li>
            <p class="Image">
                <img src="../Resources/Images/ControlloParametri_file/image039_EN.jpg" style="float: none;border-style: none;width: 521px;height: 335px;border-style: none;" width="521" height="335" border="0" />
            </p>
            <li style="margin-left: 8px;" class="p-InlineNormal19" value="2">
                <p class="InlineNormal19">Click <b>Enable notifications</b>.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="p" value="3">
                <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/save_button.png" style="width: 24px;height: 28px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="24" height="28" border="0" /><b>Save [2]</b>.</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <div style="border-top: solid #000000 1.0pt;border-left: none;border-bottom: solid #000000 1.0pt;border-right: none;padding: 5.0pt 0cm 5.0pt 0cm;float: none;background-color: #cccccc;">
            <p>
                <img src="../Resources/Images/AAinfo.gif" style="width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />&#160; Enabling only effects notifications. To temporarily disable parameter control, for example during maintenance, stop it (see <a href="Controllo_Parametri__Avviare_fermare_il_monitoraggio_dei_parametri_critici.htm">Stopping Parameter control</a>). A permanent warning is displayed to remind Service that parameter control is disabled.&#160;</p>
        </div>
        <p class="ActionDetail">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAvedianche.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />See also</p>
        <p><a href="Controllo_parametri___introduzione.htm">Parameter control: introduction</a>
        </p>
